data.description: Beautiful home & resort-style backyard all in one package! Backyard has a heated pool & spa with a real rock water feature. With no homes behind, this backyard is very private. Extended covered patio kitchen has granite countertops & stainless steel appliances. Home has updated flooring & is freshly painted in neutral colors. Open floor plan features a lg great room, kitchen island w/ walk-in pantry, dining, office/den or Man Cave & powder room. Upstairs is equally impressive with 4 bedrooms, loft & 2 full baths. Master retreat is split from the other bedrooms & master bath features double sinks, separate shower & tub and 2 walk-in closets. Well-maintained home has 2 high efficiency 16-seer A/C units. Solar System to reduce electric bills. No HOA AND DUCTLESS MINI SPLIT IN GARAGE
